    <p>Clicking the button below will generate a new FCRM1 for the entire set of projects in PAFS. This will take a long time to complete.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="form-group headroom">
  <%= button_to "Generate FCRM1 for all projects", admin_download_path, method: :post, class: "govuk-button" %>
</div>
